Deploy the new quotation PDF design to the *Salesforce production environment*. This includes database updates, entity creation, data population, and documentation of the deployment process.

*Acceptance Criteria (AC):*

# Develop and execute *unit tests* to ensure stability and correctness.
# *Migrate new entities*:
#* {{Region}}
#* {{Continent}}
# *Create a new Product* with the following attributes:
#* {{DBVersion}}: *2025-OIS-2*
#* {{Name}}: *Analysis Required*
# *Create new objects:*
#* {{SFP_Region}}
#* {{SFP_Continent}}
# *Populate new objects* with initial data:
#* {{SFP_Region}}
#* {{SFP_Continent}}
# *Populate IDs in the Country object*:
#* Add the {{Continent Id}} reference.
# *Deploy the implementation to the Production environment.*
# *Record a short video* demonstrating the deployment and the new PDF design in production.

